$ Csound: init pass
@ init pass

An init pass is triggered by an → Kunst/Musik/Csound/event to initiate an → Kunst/Musik/Csound/instrument.

{ Initializing global variables etc #initialize-global-vars

  At the start up of csound, the → Kunst/Musik/Csound/instrument#instrument-0[instrument 0] is initiazlied which processes all statements
  outside instruments.

}

sa:
  → Kunst/Musik/Csound/performance-pass
